Eco-Smart City project.
Project Title
Eco-Smart City: AI for Traffic & Green Spaces

Summary
Eco-Smart City uses AI to cut traffic jams, boost green spaces, and optimize energy in urban areas. It predicts traffic, adjusts lights, and manages waste.

Background
- Problem 1: Traffic congestion & pollution
- Problem 2: Inefficient energy & waste management
- Personal motivation: Create sustainable cities
- Importance: Greener, happier cities ðŸš€

How is it used?
- AI predicts traffic via cameras/GPS.
- Adjusts lights, suggests routes.
- Manages waste, street lights.
- Users: City planners, drivers, citizens.
