Data sources and AI methods
- Data: Cameras, sensors, GPS.
- Methods: Computer Vision, ML predictions.

Challenges
- Data privacy concerns
- Needs constant updates
- Ethical: equitable access

What next?
- Expand to more cities
- Add more AI features (water mgmt, air quality)
- Need: More data scientists, city partnerships

